  <brief_title>Study of S-1 Plus LV for Untreated Metastatic Colorectal Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of S-1 Plus LV (1 Week on and 1 Week Off) as First-line Treatment for Patients With Metastatic Colorectal Cancer</official_title>
