  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter study designed to evaluate the response rate of S-1 plus Leucovorin (1
      week on and 1 week off) as first -line treatment for patients with metastatic colorectal
      cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
